to construct a Cardy-Verlinde formula in the form of equation
(). However, as noted in  this will be impossible
if one attempts to include all the Gauss-Bonnet corrections.

Before we lose hope, it is important to take stock of what we are
actually trying to do. We are trying to find a Cardy-Verlinde formula
for a CFT that is dual to a Gauss-Bonnet AdS bulk. It only makes sense
to think of this CFT when the holographic description is valid, that
is when . It is therefore inappropriate to
include the  correction in the entropy formula
(). In the holographic limit we can make the following
